  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 29eba545bae127f488175478b5cdcb00, type: 3}
  m_Name: FlyingSkullDialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NpcDialogue
  npcName: Skull Spirit
  dialogueLines:
  - Congratulations, traveller! You have unlocked the ability to jump in this island.
    Pressing space will temporarily allow you to cross over hazards, like lava.
  - Before we can celebrate, you must help seal the fracture. It has caused the dormant
    volcanos to erupt, leaving the island covered in molten lava.
  - Follow the path to the castle, where you will find a chest. Inside it, there
    is a key that will help you seal the fracture.
  - Tread carefully, as touching lava will deplete your health.
  - Good luck, and be weary of enemies along the way.
